'''珍妮弗·安妮·道德纳'''（{{lang-en|'''Jennifer Anne Doudna'''}}，{{bd|1964年|2月19日|||}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.britannica.com/biography/Jennifer-Doudna|title=Jennifer Doudna – American biochemist|website=[[Encyclopædia_Britannica_Online|Encyclopædia Britannica Online]]|accessdate=13 November 2015|archive-date=2018-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619142235/https://www.britannica.com/biography/Jennifer-Doudna|dead-url=no}}</ref>），美国生物学家，美国[[加州大学伯克利分校|加州大学伯克利分校]]的[[化学|化学]]及[[生物学|生物学]]教授<ref name="NYT-20150511">{{cite news |last=Pollack |first=Andrew |title=Jennifer Doudna, a Pioneer Who Helped Simplify Genome Editing |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/12/science/jennifer-doudna-crispr-cas9-genetic-engineering.html |date=May 11, 2015 |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=May 12, 2015 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413233656/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/12/science/jennifer-doudna-crispr-cas9-genetic-engineering.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；自1997年以来，也担任[[霍华德·休斯医学研究所|霍华德·休斯医学研究所]]（HHMI）的研究员<ref name=nascast>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nasonline.org/news-and-multimedia/podcasts/interviews/jennifer-doudna.html |title=Interview from the National Academy of Science |access-date=2015-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151218205247/http://www.nasonline.org/news-and-multimedia/podcasts/interviews/jennifer-doudna.html |archive-date=2015-12-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=pnasbio>{{Cite journal|doi=10.1073/pnas.0408147101|title=Biography of Jennifer A. Doudna|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|volume=101|issue=49|pages=16987|year=2004|last1=Marino|first1=M.}}</ref><ref name=scopus>{{Scopus|id=7006285665}}</ref>。她与法国科学家[[埃玛纽埃勒·沙尔庞捷|埃玛纽埃勒·沙尔庞捷]]一同获得2020年[[诺贝尔化学奖|诺贝尔化学奖]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=The Nobel Prize in Chemistry 2020 |url=https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/chemistry/2020/summary/ |website=NobelPrize.org |access-date=2020-10-07 |archive-date=2020-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007095908/https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/chemistry/2020/summary/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

道德纳在[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]][[希洛_(夏威夷州)|希洛]]长大。她于1985年毕业于[[波莫纳学院|波莫纳学院]]，并于1989年从[[哈佛医学院|哈佛医学院]]毕业获得博士学位。除了她在[[加州大学伯克利分校|加州大学伯克利分校]]的教授职位之外，她还是创新基因组学研究所（Innovative Genomics Institute）的主席兼董事会主席，[[劳伦斯伯克利国家实验室|劳伦斯伯克利国家实验室]]的教职科学家，{{le|格拉德斯通研究所|Gladstone Institutes}}的高级研究员，以及[[加利福尼亚大学旧金山分校|加利福尼亚大学旧金山分校]]的细胞和分子药理学教授<ref>{{cite web |title=UC Berkeley's Jennifer Doudna wins 2020 Nobel Prize in Chemistry |url=https://news.berkeley.edu/2020/10/07/jennifer-doudna-wins-2020-nobel-prize-in-chemistry/ |publisher=University of California, Berkeley |accessdate=10 October 2020 |archive-date=2020-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007145404/https://news.berkeley.edu/2020/10/07/jennifer-doudna-wins-2020-nobel-prize-in-chemistry/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Langelier |first1=Julie |title=Jennifer Doudna Opens Laboratory at the Gladstone Institutes |url=https://gladstone.org/about-us/press-releases/jennifer-doudna-opens-laboratory-gladstone-institutes |website=Gladstone Institutes |language=en |date=September 5, 2018 |access-date=2020-11-27 |archive-date=2018-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181010011117/https://gladstone.org/about-us/press-releases/jennifer-doudna-opens-laboratory-gladstone-institutes |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=scopus>{{Scopus|id=7006285665}}</ref><ref name=gs>{{Google Scholar id}}</ref>。

